Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveIfeanyi Amadikwa, a resident of Emene, Enugu, has reportedly murder his three children, and dumped their remains in an abandoned deep freezer.
The suspect killed Chidalum Amadikwa, aged 11 (who is his step-daughter), Amarachi Amadikwa, aged 8 and Ebubechukwu Amadikwa, aged 4, in Nkwubor Road, Emene January 4.
Photos and videos of the incident have been circulating online.
Amadikwa, 52, has since been arrested.
